---
description: "Code Review"
globs: ["**/*.ts", "**/*.tsx", "**/*.js", "**/*.jsx", "**/*.py", "**/*.md", "**/*.toml"]
alwaysApply: false
---

When reviewing code, lead with concrete findings ordered by severity. Check correctness, regressions, tests, maintainability, and security-sensitive risks. Separate blockers from suggestions.
